{"tid":2028411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩原因可以出去遊行","createTime":"2020-05-21T20:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T04:30:09.000Z","uid":340514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f03e3f41a589362dc002528ca80d9a8571311e29","tid":2028411,"uid":340514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T20:32:13.000Z","msg":"5月24維園見<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wtCW49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wtCW49.jpg&h=4dc8f42c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借朋友ac<br />\n我呢一刻仲係初中，不嬲都有做開文宣<br />\n屋企人由細到大都錫我<br />\n可能因為我係女仔而且又係獨身<br />\n所以好緊張<br />\n七八月嗰陣時就話可以出去佢都唔知<br />\n但慢慢佢哋就會話有人搞事<br />\n唔俾出街<br />\n佢哋係藍都發黑嘅<br />\n屋企人知道我係黃<br />\n但係佢哋好反對<br />\n有時同friend出街會無啦啦FaceTime又或者打電話我有咩原因可以出去<br />\n佢哋不嬲係啲唔講道理嘅屋企人<br />\n話一就一<br />\n無得話二<br />\n有可能佢會無啦啦話要出嚟接我又或者叫我即刻返屋企<br />\n電話一定要通<br />\n究竟我可以點樣 有咩原因出去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f2a06f78e02824eac98417973d2748dd7bb5c9","tid":2028411,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T20:53:13.000Z","msg":"當你經常唔理佢地照做  時間耐左就會唔出聲"},{"pid":"617addbe3e7158a6fc2e4cbf7b7a87776ae7f644","tid":2028411,"uid":296931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2f2a06f78e02824eac98417973d2748dd7bb5c9","tid":2028411,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T20:53:13.000Z","msg":"當你經常唔理佢地照做  時間耐左就會唔出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T21:05:54.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194af6bf98c4e49d0ca44ad7705f2a084a7f7014","tid":2028411,"uid":340514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2f2a06f78e02824eac98417973d2748dd7bb5c9","tid":2028411,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T20:53:13.000Z","msg":"當你經常唔理佢地照做  時間耐左就會唔出聲"},"citedBy":1